parameters: \e[3]The kingdom-sanctioned magic academy gets all
the good artifacts. Aurealis Academy can only afford
the low-tier stuff...
\e[31]Don't disturb me. I'm trying to figure something
out here...
\e[4]Even these books don’t tell us where magical
artifacts originally came from, but they do tell us one
thing.
The more powerful they are, the more dangerous
they can be.
Some of them were imbued with so much power,
they’re said to have taken on a life of their own...
\e[5]Wasn’t Esper with us a few minutes ago? Where
did she sneak off to?
\e[5]Should you really be here?
Well, I guess anyone can sneak off anywhere now
that the teachers are gone...
\e[6]Hey, no fair... the book says this necklace should
let me breathe fire, but it’s not working!
\e[8]This book is full of really interesting stuff.
Swords that shoot lightning, a legendary staff that
can control water...
I wish we had some of these here, but a lot of
artifacts have been lost to history.
\e[9]There are certain kinds of artifacts that you can
wear around your neck to block your magical
power...
But why would anyone ever want to do that?
